00:39:16,446 --> 00:39:24,681
right, do everything that is necessary. But
once it is made and the light comes into it,

224
00:39:24,706 --> 00:39:37,593
then the job of the light is to give the light.
So the first function is over.

225
00:39:41,217 --> 00:39:48,217
Now the second function is to give it back.

226
00:39:48,666 --> 00:39:55,216
You reach your aim, your destination. For
