00:40:11,565 --> 00:40:25,074
time running. So, all this mad race of this
brain stops. For what should it be used now?

230
00:40:26,176 --> 00:40:38,711
For enjoying the peace, for enjoying the joy,
for enjoying the collectivity. So, the labour

231
00:40:38,736 --> 00:40:47,441
or the hard work or you can also say the planning
of the future finishes off. Only thing now

232
00:40:47,466 --> 00:40:51,476
you have got it, so better enjoy it.

233
00:40:51,476 --> 00:41:03,681
It’s like you are coming from outside, you
are running, you are very hungry, you want

234
00:41:03,706 --> 00:41:13,111
to reach home. Once you reach home, then the
food is served to you. Now what's your aim?

235
00:41:13,136 --> 00:41:19,256
Nothing, but to enjoy the food for which you
were running. But after that also, if you

236
00:41:19,256 --> 00:41:30,141
start running, then one should say it is absolute
stupidity! But the capacity of enjoyment only

237
00:41:30,166 --> 00:41:41,720
comes when your Sahastrara is absolutely open.
Otherwise the capacity to enjoy is much less

238
00:41:42,636 --> 00:41:50,217
and you become like a person who is running
all the time after something which you never

239
00:41:50,242 --> 00:41:58,411
achieve. There are many like that. All their
lives they’re like mad, you know. They are

240
00:41:58,436 --> 00:42:06,580
working morning till evening, everyday, achieving
nothing! Next day again get up, again running!

241
00:42:06,605 --> 00:42:13,605
All their lives running like this till their
foot is in the grave, they are still running.

242
00:42:15,845 --> 00:42:25,050
But after getting to Sahaja Yoga, you stop
all these activities and leave it to your

243
00:42:25,075 --> 00:42:36,527
Sahaja Yoga to work, to your Sahastrara to
work it out. And it works out. You don't have

244
00:42:36,552 --> 00:42:41,956
to rush. You don't have to be so competent.
You don't have to write down everything. You

245
00:42:41,981 --> 00:42:48,620
don't have to think of planning everything.
Just everything works out and it works out

246
00:42:48,645 --> 00:42:54,696
beautifully. The only thing that one has to
do is to accept whatever is happening for

247
00:42:54,696 --> 00:43:08,249
our good. Even in small, small things. For
today's delay in the puja, is the desire of

